<paragraph id="086868DA09205398FBEB057BDA58AD91" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Brazil • 1 ♂; Rondonia, 62 km SE Ariquemes; 8-20 Nov. 1994; W.J. Hanson leg.; LACM.</paragraph>
